channel.title: Axoloti on SoundCloud
channel.description:
I've opened a SoundCloud account to share the sounds from my book, and some other things I've created with Axoloti. Only four clips for now, but there's more coming soon: https://soundcloud.com/janvantomme
There is also an official Axoloti group on SoundCloud, so please join and post the music you made with Axoloti to the group: https://soundcloud.com/groups/axoloti
If you have a SoundCloud account, post a link to it in this topic, as It's always great to discover new music.
You can find some of my music over here: https://soundcloud.com/jayvanz
